      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional example of the S54-powered icon, preserved in showroom condition. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This unit features a reinforced rear subframe and has undergone a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring mechanical longevity. The factory-spec limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution, while the chassis remains taut and responsive. Finished in original paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver.",
